snippet.description:
A little boy, desperate for his sick mother’s recovery, fell to his knees in front of a living Jesus statue, praying with all his heart. While other kids mocked him, his father stood by his side. But then, something unexpected happened—the statue stepped down and invited them to pray together. Was it just an act, or something more?

snippet.title: Sa Bawat Sandali - Amiel Sol (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
The Official Music Video of "Sa Bawat Sandali" by Amiel Sol.

Starring Andres Muhlach and Ashtine Olviga
#AmielSolSBSMV #AshDresSBSMV #SaBawatSandaliMV #AAASaBawatSandali

Amiel Sol is back with a brand new single, “Sa Bawat Sandali.” It is a heartfelt ballad that dives deep into the themes of love, longing, and treasuring every fleeting moment. With tender lyrics and a gentle melody, the track captures the beauty and vulnerability of holding on to precious times with someone special. Amiel’s emotive voice draws listeners in, making each line feel personal and sincere, as he reflects on the timelessness of love even amidst the passage of time. Perfect for those quiet moments of reflection, “Sa Bawat Sandali” invites fans to savor each second with the ones they cherish.
